(- Key and Signature Size Policy) Tj
T*
(From Src/Utility/const.py:) Tj
T*
(- Canonical Falcon pubkey size: 897 bytes \(FALCON_PUBKEY_BYTES\).) Tj
T*
(- Legacy pubkey size \(compatibility\): 1024 bytes \(FALCON_PUBKEY_LEGACY_BYTES\), currently) Tj
